rows.label: qst610507_msg0002
rows.name:
You really saved my skin.
Thanks a bunch.

rows.label: qst610507_msg0004
rows.name:
I could only take out about half
of the blighters.

rows.label: qst610507_msg0005
rows.name:
I'm lucky you lot were here to help,
that's all I can say.

rows.label: qst610507_msg0006
rows.name:
Thanks to you, we were able to keep
our losses to a minimum.

rows.label: qst610507_msg0007
rows.name:
I thought this place was a bore, but
maybe there are some thrills to be had
after all.

rows.label: qst610507_msg0008
rows.name:
It's not like back home...these are the
front lines. Anything can happen!

rows.label: qst610507_msg0009
rows.name:
I'll make sure to keep an extra-sharp
lookout in future.

rows.label: qst610507_msg0010
rows.name:
By the by, I'm guessing it was the
Captain that sent ye here, right?

rows.label: qst610507_msg0011
rows.name:
We can handle the rest, so you oughtta
head back and give him a full report.

rows.label: qst610507_msg0012
rows.name:
Tell him old Irving is set to become the
Bathein of Temperantia!
